# Titanic Survival Prediction — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# This project does not require API keys for local use.

# --- Optional: Hugging Face deployment ---
# Required only when deploying to Hugging Face Spaces via GitHub Actions.
# Create a token at https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# Then add it as a GitHub Actions secret named HF_TOKEN.
# HF_TOKEN=hf_your_token_here
